        Transfer Duty in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know About Buyer Costs
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Transfer duty is one of the largest upfront costs a Queensland buyer faces. Understanding how it works helps sellers read their buyer pool more accurately and negotiate with more information.
      </p>
